    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed and all achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 5. Discretization error achieved level 5 (required 4), providing additional confidence margin. Model form and model inputs factors demonstrate rigorous multi-model ensemble and Monte Carlo UQ with Sobol sensitivity analysis. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU geometry and operating envelope. PIV velocity field and hemolysis bench comparisons both confirm predictive capability within quantified uncertainty bounds. The complete provenance chain from raw experimental data through validation results to this decision record is documented and traceable. The package satisfies all requirements for the Complete profile under ASME V&V 40 at MRL 5.",
